items.title: Awesome Prometheus
items.content_text:
### Proxies / Miscellaneous

*   [PromQL Guard (⭐25)](https://github.com/kfdm/promql-guard) - Provides a thin proxy on top of Prometheus, that allows PromQL queries to be inspected and re-written, so that a tenant can only see allowed data, even when using a shared Prometheus server.
items.content_html:
Proxies / Miscellaneous

  • PromQL Guard (⭐25) - Provides a thin proxy on top of Prometheus, that allows PromQL queries to be inspected and re-written, so that a tenant can only see allowed data, even when using a shared Prometheus server.
